---
const tools = [
  "Google Calendar",
  "WhatsApp Business",
  "Calendar / iCal",
  "Email",
  "CRM",
  "Sito web",
];
---

<section class="section integ" id="integrazioni">
  <div class="container integ__inner">
    <div class="integ__copy" data-reveal>
      <h2>Si collega a ciò che usi già.</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        SofIA si sincronizza con il tuo calendario e i tuoi strumenti. Niente
        da reinventare: si innesta sul flusso di lavoro che hai oggi.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul class="integ__grid" aria-label="Strumenti integrati">
      {tools.map((t) => (
        <li class="integ__tool">
          <span class="integ__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          {t}
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .integ__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 1rem + 4vw, 4rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .integ__copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 34rem;
  }
  .integ__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .integ__tool {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .integ__tool:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .integ__dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: var(--coral);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .integ__tool:nth-child(even) .integ__dot {
    background: var(--green);
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .integ__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
